_sText:
This is a perfect GunGame map!
It feels a lot like churches, but with an amazing courtyard feel with nicer all-around looks and gameplay. There is plenty of cover, not too many camping spots and no chances of early spawn-killing. Each side has its own small tower for those nasty sniper levels, and the center tower has an extra 2 grenades, but the tower is only accessible by hopping from one hedge to another.

Instant classic!

40 total spawn points, 20 for each team.

Great for downloading, as it is only roughly 1 mb!
